PrecisEnactment of the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (VUNTUT GWITCHIN FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of specific lands in the Yukon Territory in order to facilitate the settlement of native land claims made by the Vuntut Gwitchin First Nation.
